at least be a credit
to your own kind...

1039
01:17:47,412 --> 01:17:49,631
and beat every foul
thought from them.

1040
01:17:58,298 --> 01:17:59,641
(SCREAMING)

1041
01:18:00,091 --> 01:18:01,092
Beat it from them!

1042
01:18:05,722 --> 01:18:07,190
(PATSEY WHIMPERING)

1043
01:18:18,277 --> 01:18:19,118
MISTRESS EPPS: Eat.

1044
01:18:20,362 --> 01:18:21,988
Fill yourselves.

1045
01:18:22,780 --> 01:18:24,033
And then we dance.

1046
01:18:29,329 --> 01:18:31,707
I said, eat.

1047
01:18:36,502 --> 01:18:38,130
