1054
01:19:09,578 --> 01:19:10,328
Return it.

1055
01:19:10,496 --> 01:19:12,168
It yours, Platt.

1056
01:19:13,498 --> 01:19:15,171
For what cause?

1057
01:19:15,333 --> 01:19:19,510
All I ask, end my life.

1058
01:19:20,713 --> 01:19:23,934
Take my body to
the margin of the swamp.

1059
01:19:24,092 --> 01:19:27,096
