1063
01:19:35,436 --> 01:19:37,189
The gory detail
with which you speak...

1064
01:19:37,355 --> 01:19:39,859
I thought on it long and hard.

1065
01:19:41,234 --> 01:19:43,203
It is melancholia.

1066
01:19:43,779 --> 01:19:45,280
Nothing more.

1067
01:19:46,448 --> 01:19:49,247
How can you fall
into such despair?

1068
01:19:49,409 --> 01:19:52,458
How can you not know?

1069
01:19:54,581 --> 01:19:58,551
I ain't got no
comfort in this life.

1070
01:20:00,878 --> 01:20:04,884
If I can't buy mercy from you...

1071
01:20:05,050 --> 01:20:07,144
I'll beg it.

1072
01:20:07,302 --> 01:20:08,895
There are others.

1073
01:20:09,930 --> 01:20:11,398
